--perform-motion-correction
Enable motion correction (optional)
--show-plots

div.div:
Processing Steps:
1. load_dataset: Load NIfTI + build gradient table from bval/bvec
2. denoise_nlmeans: PIESNO estimates noise level, NLMEANS applies non-local means denoising
3. background_segmentation: median_otsu on b0 volumes creates brain mask
4. perform_motion_correction (optional): Between-volume rigid registration
5. save_output: Writes preprocessed data + copies gradient files
Coil Count (N):
N=4 for GRAPPA parallel imaging
N=1 for SENSE parallel imaging
